Past Events

     * ROSSI 2000
       NASA Goddard Space Flight Center
       March 22-24, 2000
     * Second Ultra Long Duration Ballooning Technology Workshop
       November 12 - 13, 1998
       Goddard Space Flight Center
     * Ultra High Energy Cosmic-ray Workshop: "Observing Giant Cosmic Ray
       Airshowers for > 10^20 eV Particles from Space"
       November 13-15, 1997
     * Ultra Long Duration Ballooning Workshop, June 24-25, 1997
       NASA at Goddard Space Flight Center, Greenbelt, Md.
     * X-ray Surveys Workshop: June 18-20, 1997.
     * The Fourth COMPTON Symposium on Gamma-Ray Astrophysics: April
       27-30, 1997,
       Williamsburg,Va.
     * Structure & Evolution of the Universe Technology Workshop: December
       2-3, 1996
     * Prospects for 100 Day Balloon Flights Workshop: October 31 -
       November 1, 1996.

